	<plot>Overview:Marmalade Boy is a dating sim game that was  released only in Japan and based on a popular anime of the same name. Marmalade Boy was originally released on the    Game Boy system, and later released on the    Super Famicom.  In Marmalade  Boy the player assumes the role of Miki.  As Miki the player must try and  win the affections of one of three characters: Yuu, Ginta, and Kei.</plot>
